# Updater signing keys must never be committed. The real private key lives
# outside the repo (e.g. ~/.tauri/mite-updater.key) and is loaded into CI as the
# TAURI_SIGNING_PRIVATE_KEY secret; this guards against a stray local copy.
*.key
*.key.pub
.tauri/

